                The ASP.NET Core wrapper packages the editor as a Razor Tag Helper. Add it to any form,
                map the upload endpoint, and your users get a familiar word-like editing surface.
            </p>
            <ul class="mt-8 space-y-4">
                <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
