                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                    <span class="mt-0.5 flex h-6 w-6 flex-none items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-[#0f8b8d]/10 text-[#0f8b8d]">
                        <svg class="h-3.5 w-3.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M9 16.17L4.83 12l-1.42 1.41L9 19 21 7l-1.41-1.41z"/></svg>
                    </span>
                    <span class="text-sm leading-6 text-slate-700">Built-in upload endpoint with folder-aware image gallery.</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                    <span class="mt-0.5 flex h-6 w-6 flex-none items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-[#0f8b8d]/10 text-[#0f8b8d]">
                        <svg class="h-3.5 w-3.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M9 16.17L4.83 12l-1.42 1.41L9 19 21 7l-1.41-1.41z"/></svg>
                    </span>
                    <span class="text-sm leading-6 text-slate-700">Forms receive clean HTML back on submit — no extra JavaScript required.</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                    <span class="mt-0.5 flex h-6 w-6 flex-none items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-[#0f8b8d]/10 text-[#0f8b8d]">
                        <svg class="h-3.5 w-3.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M9 16.17L4.83 12l-1.42 1.41L9 19 21 7l-1.41-1.41z"/></svg>
                    </span>
                    <span class="text-sm leading-6 text-slate-700">Toolbar presets, skins, resize modes — all configurable via Tag Helper attributes.</span>
                </li>
            </ul>
            <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-4">
                <a asp-page="/Demos" class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full bg-[#0f8b8d] px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-lg shadow-teal-500/20 transition hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:text-white">Try demo</a>
